org.ensembl.datamodel
Class AssemblyLocation

java.lang.Object
  org.ensembl.datamodel.Location
      org.ensembl.datamodel.AssemblyLocation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable
Deprecated. Create instances of Location directly. The specific location types such as AssemblyLocation have been superseded by the more generic Location class.

public class AssemblyLocation
extends Location

Location on an assembly. The location is specified by any or all of these properties AssemblyMap, chromosome, start, end and strand.
